Package eu.focusnet.app.ui.activity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DemoUseCaseSelectionActivity Deprecated
    only used in the prototype.
    EntryPointActivity
    Entry point activity

    Start screen of the application.
    ImageActivity
    Activity use to display an image that has been previously captured by the camera.
    LoginActivity
    Login Activity: this activity displays the login screen and let's the user log into the application.
    PageActivity
    This Activity is created when accessing a page from a project listing Activity (ProjectsListingActivity or ProjectInProjectActivity).
    ProjectActivity
    This Activity is created when accessing a project from the ProjectsListingActivity.
    ProjectInProjectActivity
    This Activity is created when a new project is to be displayed from a ProjectActivity.
    ProjectsListingActivity
    This Activity contains the listing of all projects, and is therefore the welcome screen of our application after the login and loading screens.
    ToolbarEnabledActivity
    The ToolbarEnabledActivity is used as the basis for Activities that have a title bar and a content below.
